Advanced Usage

Custom Type Composition

# Combine multiple features
ComplexType &lt;- create_list_type(list(
  id = String | Numeric,
  data = ListOf(Numeric[3]),
  metadata = Optional(create_list_type(list(
    created = String,
    tags = ListOf(String)
  )))
))



Type Guards and Validation

# Function with typed parameters
validate_user &lt;- function(user_data) {
  user_data %:% create_list_type(list(
    username = String,
    email = String,
    age = Numeric
  )) %&lt;-% user_data

  # Additional validation logic
  if (user_data$age &lt; 0) {
    stop("Age cannot be negative")
  }

  return(TRUE)
}



Integration with Existing Code
Types can be added gradually:

# Existing untyped code
existing_function &lt;- function(x) {
  return(x * 2)
}

# Add typing where needed
typed_function &lt;- function(input) {
  input %:% Numeric %&lt;-% input
  result &lt;- existing_function(input)
  result %:% Numeric %&lt;-% result
  return(result)
}
